org.apache.poi.common.usermodel.fonts

Enum FontFamily

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<FontFamily>
      • org.apache.poi.common.usermodel.fonts.FontFamily
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<FontFamily> 

    public enum FontFamily
extends java.lang.Enum<FontFamily>
    A property of a font that describes its general appearance.(字体的属性，描述其一般外观。)
    Since:
    POI 3.17-beta2

    • Enum Constant Summary

      Enum Constants 
      Enum Constant and Description
      FF_DECORATIVE
      Novelty fonts.(新颖的字体。)
      FF_DONTCARE
      The default font is specified, which is implementation-dependent.(指定了默认字体，该字体取决于实现。)
      FF_MODERN
      Fonts with constant stroke width, with or without serifs.(笔画宽度恒定的字体，有或没有衬线。)
      FF_ROMAN
      Fonts with variable stroke widths, which are proportional to the actual widths of the glyphs, and which have serifs.(笔画宽度可变的字体，与字形的实际宽度成比例，并且具有衬线。)
      FF_SCRIPT
      Fonts designed to look like handwriting.(字体设计得看起来像手写的。)
      FF_SWISS
      Fonts with variable stroke widths, which are proportional to the actual widths of the glyphs, and which do not have serifs.(笔画宽度可变的字体，与字形的实际宽度成比例，并且没有衬线。)

    • Enum Constant Detail

      • FF_DONTCARE

        public static final FontFamily FF_DONTCARE
        The default font is specified, which is implementation-dependent.(指定了默认字体，该字体取决于实现。)

      • FF_ROMAN

        public static final FontFamily FF_ROMAN
        Fonts with variable stroke widths, which are proportional to the actual widths of the glyphs, and which have serifs. "MS Serif" is an example.(笔画宽度可变的字体，与字形的实际宽度成比例，并且具有衬线。“MS Serif”就是一个例子。)

      • FF_SWISS

        public static final FontFamily FF_SWISS
        Fonts with variable stroke widths, which are proportional to the actual widths of the glyphs, and which do not have serifs. "MS Sans Serif" is an example.(笔画宽度可变的字体，与字形的实际宽度成比例，并且没有衬线。“MS Sans Serif”就是一个例子。)

      • FF_MODERN

        public static final FontFamily FF_MODERN
        Fonts with constant stroke width, with or without serifs. Fixed-width fonts are usually modern. "Pica", "Elite", and "Courier New" are examples.(笔画宽度恒定的字体，有或没有衬线。固定宽度字体通常是现代的。“Pica”、“Elite”和“Courier New”就是例子。)

      • FF_SCRIPT

        public static final FontFamily FF_SCRIPT
        Fonts designed to look like handwriting. "Script" and "Cursive" are examples.(字体设计得看起来像手写的。“脚本”和“草书”就是例子。)

      • FF_DECORATIVE

        public static final FontFamily FF_DECORATIVE
        Novelty fonts. "Old English" is an example.(新颖的字体。“古英语”就是一个例子。)
